## Seed initial data

```bash id="pcd93d"
python seed_data.py
Management helper

Run server:

python manage.py runserver

Run migrations:

python manage.py migrate

Run tests:

python manage.py test

Seed demo data:

python manage.py seed

Run grading worker:

python manage.py worker

Run expiry auto-submit:

python manage.py expiry

```make id="3u52zu"
expiry:
	python -m app.workers.grading_jobs --expiry-check
	
	
	
